title: OnboardingIntro
tags:
--- 
<<talking_instructor_animation YarnCommands>> //start the instructors talking animation
Hello and welcome to the d/Deaf Awareness Empathy Sim! //introduces the player to the simulation

Before you start your immersive experience, //lets the player know that they will be going through an onboarding tutorial
you must first learn how to use an XR application.  

Would you like to go through the onboarding tutorial? //asks the player if they would like to go through the onboarding tutorial
<<stop_talking_instructor_animation YarnCommands>>
