title: Confirmation
tags:
---
<<stop_talking_instructor_animation YarnCommands>> //stops the instructors talking animation
Are you sure you want to skip the onboarding tutorial? //asks the player if they are sure they want to skip the onboarding tutorial
<<stop_talking_instructor_animation YarnCommands>>

